text: Jolo is a city which is the capital of the Sulu province of the Philippines. In 2015, 125,564 people lived there. That same year, 40% of people living there were poor. Islamist bombers attacked Jolo in 2019 and 2020. ==References== Category:Cities in the Philippines Category:Provincial capitals of the Philippines Category:Sulu
title: Jolo, Sulu
